<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Instruction Brochure - How Our Website Works</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-zinc-900">

    <!-- Header -->
    <header class="bg-gray-800 text-white py-4 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold">How Our Website Works</h1>
    </header>

    <!-- Section -->
    <section class="bg-zinc-800 max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">1. Getting Started</h2>
        <p class="text-white mb-4">To begin using our website, follow these steps:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white">
            <li>Sign up for an account using your email or social login options.</li>
            <li>Complete your profile by providing necessary details.</li>
            <li>Explore the dashboard to access various features.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. Navigating the Dashboard</h2>
        <p class="text-white mb-4">Our dashboard is designed to provide a seamless experience with the following features:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white">
            <li><strong>Search Jobs:</strong> View, create, and manage custom Projects for skills enhancement.</li>
            <li><strong>Projects Completed:</strong> Gives a Tab about the number of Projects Completed.</li>
            <li><strong>Wallet:</strong> Gives an account about the principal generated.</li>
            <li><strong>Notifications:</strong> Gives an account about the status of the project.</li>
            <li><strong>View your Profile:</strong>Can View or Edit your profile and also view your Programming Skills .</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. Submitting Assignments</h2>
        <p class="text-white mb-4">To submit an assignment or task, follow these steps:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white">
            <li>Select the task from the assigned tasks on the dashboard.</li>
            <li>Click on "Submit" and upload your file.</li>
            <li>Ensure your submission follows the given guidelines.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. Instructor's Role</h2>
        <p class="text-white mb-4">If you're an instructor, you have the ability to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-white">
            <li>Create learning paths and assign them to learners.</li>
            <li>Monitor student progress and provide feedback.</li>
            <li>Update assignments and track submission status.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mt-8 mb-4">5.Reviews and Ratings</h2>
        <p class="text-white">The Freelancer would be rated and reviewed based on his/her previous projects</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-gray-800 text-white text-center py-4 mt-8">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Freelancer's Hub. All Rights Reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>